   <text type="letter">
      <body>
         
            <opener rend="right">
               <dateline>
                  <name type="place">Department of the Interior,<lb/>
Washington, D. C.,</name>
                  <date when="1865-05-11">May 11, 1865.</date>
               </dateline>
            </opener>
            <p>Walt Whitman of New York is hereby promoted to a Clerkship of the Second Class in the Office of Indian Affairs to take effect from and after the first instant.</p>  
            <closer rend="right">
               <signed>William T. Otto, <lb/> Assistant Secretary of the Interior.<ptr target="nyp.00221_n100"/>
            </signed>
            </closer>
         
      </body>
